                <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
                    Designing, installing, and maintaining advanced security systems including access control, CCTV, fire alarms, fire suppression, intruder alarms, and perimeter protection.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    Smart, integrated solutions ensuring maximum safety for your premises.
                </p>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Services", "User")" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 1px solid #f39c12; background-color: #f39c12; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Book Service</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
