                    Providing guarding, fire squad, dog squad, and personal bodyguards for industries, banks, retail outlets, residential colonies, hotels, and institutions.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    Ensuring the highest standards of protection through skilled and dedicated personnel.
                </p>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Services", "User")" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 1px solid #f39c12; background-color: #f39c12; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Book Service</a>
